title: ABBA - Lay All Your Love On Me (Disconet Mix Re-created)
description:
This is the best remix of ABBA - Lay All Your Love On Me. Original vinyl of this mix is worth around $300, so why bother to get it?

So I got a VERY nice version of the internet (from vinyl of course) and recreated it, using latest remaster from 2005 (complete studio recordings). It sound alomoast as the original one, but without all cracs an pops and nose comming from vinyl. 

You got here the original uncompressed Wav file in a rar archive, which makes the file 25 % smaller.


Enjoy this piece of music!
